text: Icon Towers is a multi functional complex of two under construction skyscraper, named as Icon Tower 1 and 2 at Setiabudi, South Jakarta, Indonesia. This is a mixed complex for hotel, residence and office. Tower 1 has 78 floors and 350 meters height, where as Tower 2 has 58 floors and 195.2 meters height. The complex has a podium of 15 floors to connect two tower. The complex was expected to be completed by 2019. ==See also== * List of tallest buildings in Indonesia * List of tallest buildings in Jakarta ==References== ==External links== * Building at The Skyscraper Center database * Building at Emporis database Category:Towers in Indonesia Category:Buildings and structures in Jakarta Category:Skyscrapers in Indonesia Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Indonesia
